'''真菌呼腸孤病毒屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Mycoreovirus''）是[[呼腸孤病毒科|呼腸孤病毒科]]{{le|刺突呼腸孤病毒亞科|Spinareovirinae}}的一個[[屬|屬]]，包含MyRV1、MyRV2與MyRV3三種病毒，皆為[[真菌病毒|真菌病毒]]，其中MyRV1與MyRV2自{{le|栗枝枯病菌|Cryphonectria parasitica}}分離，MyRV3則自[[棕墊炭豆菌|棕墊炭豆菌]]分離<ref name="TanakaEusebio-Cope2012"/>。

==病毒學==
本屬病毒不具有[[病毒包膜|包膜]]，直徑約為80奈米，[[基因組|基因組]]為分段的線型雙股[[RNA|RNA]]，MyRV1與MyRV2的基因組分為11段，MyRV3的則分為12段<ref name="TanakaEusebio-Cope2012">{{cite journal|last1=Tanaka|first1=Toru|last2=Eusebio-Cope|first2=Ana|last3=Sun|first3=Liying|last4=Suzuki|first4=Nobuhiro|title=Mycoreovirus Genome Alterations: Similarities to and Differences from Rearrangements Reported for Other Reoviruses|journal=Frontiers in Microbiology|volume=3|year=2012|issn=1664-302X|doi=10.3389/fmicb.2012.00186}}</ref>，長度介於0.7－4.1[[鹼基對|kb]]之間，每一段都包含一個[[開放閱讀框|開放閱讀框]]編碼蛋白質，最長者（4.1kb）為編碼[[RNA複製酶|RNA複製酶]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://viralzone.expasy.org/630|title=Mycoreovirus|publisher=ViralZone|access-date=2020-07-10|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207035459/https://viralzone.expasy.org/630|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==感染==
MyRV1感染{{le|栗枝枯病菌|Cryphonectria parasitica}}後，會降低後者對植物的致病能力<ref name="Eusebio-CopeSuzuki2015">{{cite journal|last1=Eusebio-Cope|first1=Ana|last2=Suzuki|first2=Nobuhiro|title=Mycoreovirus genome rearrangements associated with RNA silencing deficiency|journal=Nucleic Acids Research|volume=43|issue=7|year=2015|pages=3802–3813|issn=1362-4962|doi=10.1093/nar/gkv239}}</ref>。MyRV3感染[[棕墊炭豆菌|棕墊炭豆菌]]也會抑制其[[菌絲體|菌絲體]]的生長，進而降低其對植物的致病性<ref name="YaegashiYoshikawa2013">{{cite journal|last1=Yaegashi|first1=Hajime|last2=Yoshikawa|first2=Nobuyuki|last3=Ito|first3=Tsutae|last4=Kanematsu|first4=Satoko|title=A mycoreovirus suppresses RNA silencing in the white root rot fungus, Rosellinia necatrix|journal=Virology|volume=444|issue=1-2|year=2013|pages=409–416|issn=00426822|doi=10.1016/j.virol.2013.07.010}}</ref>。

